OL,3,COmbudsman's 'regret' as Troubles
OL,4,Camnesty law 'ends ability to provide
OL,5,Canswers'
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's Police Ombudsman
OL,8,Fhas said she plans to conclude 95
OL,9,FTroubles-related cases "in the next
OL,10,Fyear".
OL,12,FMarie Anderson was speaking as scores
OL,13,Fof legacy inquests are set to be
OL,14,Fhalted and transferred to the
OL,15,FIndependent Commission for
OL,16,FReconciliation and Information
OL,17,FRecovery (ICRIR) under the terms of
OL,18,Fthe Government's controversial Legacy
OL,19,FAct.
