OL,7,FThe Police Ombudsman's Office has
OL,8,Fdelivered a number of reports into the
OL,9,Fpast, including looking at the police
OL,10,Finvestigation into the loyalist murder
OL,11,Fof five people in the Sean Graham
OL,12,Fbookmakers shop on the Ormeau Road in
OL,13,Fsouth Belfast in 1992.
