OL,5,Canswers'
OL,7,F"I have been open about the challenges
OL,8,Fwhich have faced legacy
OL,9,Finvestigations, as have my
OL,10,Fpredecessors, who have repeatedly
OL,11,Fspoken of significant periods of
OL,12,Funderfunding and limited resources to
OL,13,Fconduct and conclude these complex
OL,14,Finvestigations, which date back
OL,15,Fdecades.
OL,17,F"I am writing personally to those
OL,18,Ffamilies whose investigations will not
OL,19,Fnow be progressed by my office,
OL,20,Fexpressing regret and I know they will
OL,21,Fbe deeply disappointed and distressed."
