OL,7,FMs Anderson added: "The investigations
OL,8,Fconducted by this office are
OL,9,Fintertwined with the history of the
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland Troubles and some of
OL,11,Fits worst atrocities.
OL,13,F"Undertaking investigations from this
OL,14,Fera means working in a contested
OL,15,Fenvironment, and navigating through
OL,16,Fthat space has required adherence to
OL,17,Fimpartiality, independence and
OL,18,Fevidence-based findings."
