OL,7,FGoing forward, Ms Anderson said her
OL,8,Foffice will be "transitioning to an
OL,9,Foversight body that focuses not only
OL,10,Fon the conduct of police officers in a
OL,11,Fcontemporary setting".
OL,13,FShe said it will also be
OL,14,F"demonstrating the impact of our work
OL,15,Fon policing policy and practice".
